Hatching Pokemon Egg Mechanic:

The user gets an egg that can be hatched after certain
a certain milestone of walking is completed.

There are 3 types of eggs:
- 2 Km hatch distance
- 5 Km hatch distance
- 10 Km hatch distance

Once the walking distance is accomplished, the egg
is hatched and the user receives one of the random
types of Pokemon.
